Interface IObjectBooleanFailer

    IFail, IObjectBooleanDefaultFail, IObjectBooleanEqualsFail, IObjectBooleanFalseFail, IObjectBooleanNotDefaultFail, IObjectBooleanNotEqualsFail, IObjectBooleanNotNullFail, IObjectBooleanNotSameFail, IObjectBooleanNullFail, IObjectBooleanSameFail, IObjectBooleanTrueFail

    public interface IObjectBooleanFailer
extends IObjectBooleanSameFail, IObjectBooleanNotSameFail, IObjectBooleanEqualsFail, IObjectBooleanNotEqualsFail, IObjectBooleanNullFail, IObjectBooleanNotNullFail, IObjectBooleanFalseFail, IObjectBooleanTrueFail, IObjectBooleanDefaultFail, IObjectBooleanNotDefaultFail
    Specification grouping all Boolean fail specifications.

    This (or a derivative) should inherit all fail methods targeting Boolean.
